00:03:59.580 --> 00:04:03.460
And, secondly, that
Thucydides is a mouthful.

00:04:03.460 --> 00:04:04.760
&gt;&gt; David M. Rubenstein:
What's the most [inaudible]--

00:04:04.760 --> 00:04:07.560
&gt;&gt; Graham Allison: Let me just
