00:04:07.560 --> 00:04:08.990
One, two, three.

00:04:08.990 --> 00:04:10.290
Thucydides.

00:04:10.290 --> 00:04:12.000
&gt;&gt; David M. Rubenstein: What is
the most interesting pronunciation

00:04:12.000 --> 00:04:13.300
you've heard?

00:04:13.300 --> 00:04:17.660
&gt;&gt; Graham Allison: Well, if you
