00:04:27.960 --> 00:04:32.150
because Chinese don't
pronounce Thucydides as--

00:04:32.150 --> 00:04:33.450
&gt;&gt; David M. Rubenstein: Okay.

00:04:33.450 --> 00:04:35.370
&gt;&gt; Graham Allison: The way
