00:04:35.370 --> 00:04:38.240
But, any case, Thucydides
was the founder of history.

00:04:38.240 --> 00:04:41.020
He wrote the first
ever history book.

00:04:41.020 --> 00:04:45.590 position:56%
So you can go download for free "The
History of the Peloponnesian War,"

00:04:45.590 --> 00:04:49.130
