00:10:22.190 --> 00:10:23.960
By 1900 they were equal.

00:10:23.960 --> 00:10:26.520
By 1914 they were recorded larger.

00:10:26.520 --> 00:10:29.230
So they were on a tear.

00:10:29.230 --> 00:10:32.200
From the point of view of Britain,
which had been the ruling power

00:10:32.200 --> 00:10:34.020
