00:10:46.930 --> 00:10:50.230
that's building up its strength,
building up its military strength,

00:10:50.230 --> 00:10:57.350
building up its Navy, impacted
Britain so severely that they began

00:10:57.350 --> 00:11:00.200
to become entangled
with third parties.

00:11:00.200 --> 00:11:02.520
So Britain became entangled
with France.

00:11:02.520 --> 00:11:05.440
France had an alliance with Russia.

00:11:05.440 --> 00:11:09.930
This created a set of
interlocking commitments such that

00:11:09.930 --> 00:11:13.600
