Soviet Union will overtake the U.S.

00:12:55.720 --> 00:12:59.700
So the fear in terms of the
impact of the Soviet Union,

00:12:59.700 --> 00:13:03.600
the missile gap, all the
things that surrounded that,

00:13:03.600 --> 00:13:10.470
