celebrate still as the wise men,

00:13:10.470 --> 00:13:14.980
people like George Kennan, who
wrote back the famous telegram,

00:13:14.980 --> 00:13:18.520
or Acheson, or Vandenberg,
the Republican leader

00:13:18.520 --> 00:13:22.330
