in a great surge

00:13:26.090 --> 00:13:30.780
of imagination a strategy they
called "The Cold War Strategy."

00:13:30.780 --> 00:13:33.800
And Cold War was competition
on every dimension,

00:13:33.800 --> 00:13:36.390
and by all means except one--

00:13:36.390 --> 00:13:39.220
no bombs and bullets
killing each other directly.

00:13:39.220 --> 00:13:43.420
So you had this extreme
competition in every dimension--

00:13:43.420 --> 00:13:49.700
economic, political, ideological,
covert action, even proxy wars,

00:13:49.700 --> 00:13:51.740
but not you and me
killing each other.

00:13:51.740 --> 00:13:55.430
And that came to some
very close calls,

00:13:55.430 --> 00:13:57.280 position:56%
as you and I've talked often before.

00:13:57.280 --> 00:14:00.610
The Cuban Missile Crisis was
about, as Kennedy thought,

00:14:00.610 --> 00:14:03.700
